HEADWORD: expansiveness
<hw>expansiveness</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a quality
characterized by magnificence of scale; <as>as, the
<ex>expansiveness</ex> of their extravagant lifestyle was soon
curtailed</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a friendly open trait of a talkative
person.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> effusiveness.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

